    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok cool, fixed. Two benefits: our new default github pages (org wise) is community.algolia.com.\n\nPeople trying to access algolia.github.io on purpose will be redirected to community.algolia.com (301, good for SEO too).\n\nSolved by:\n- adding a CNAME file to https://github.com/algolia/algolia.github.io\n- removing the cloudflare host override (otherwise infinite redirect loop)\n",
